    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Soft shoes, often of leather or leatherlike fabric, with a rounded toe and either a split or full soft sole, intended to be worn for dance. For shoes derived from the design of the dance shoe, intended as street wear, use "ballet flats."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
